          <img class="testimonial-image" id="img1" src="../images/AS.png" alt="Anushka-Sharma" />

          <h4>"I have anxiety. And I'm treating my anxiety. I'm on medication
            for my anxiety. Why am I saying this? Because it's a completely
            normal thing. It's a biological problem. In my family, there have
            been cases of depression. More and more people should talk openly
            about it. There is nothing shameful about it or something to hide.
            If you had a constant stomach pain, wouldn't you go to the doctor?
            It's that simple. I want to make this my mission, to take any
            shame out of this, to educate people about this,”</h4>

