            straight line or everything has to be in pairs. I'll put my Pepsi
            cans in the fridge and if there's one too many then I'll put it in
            another cupboard somewhere. I'll go into a hotel room and before I
            can relax, I have to move all the leaflets and all the books and
            put them in a drawer.”</h4>

          <em>~David Beckham</em>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
